  <section class="section p-xlarge text-center" id="intro">
    <p>It's often bothering, if not difficult to set up a small demo using a text or a search input. Depending on what you want to achieve, you have to set up the submit buttons, the clear buttons, the update of the value of the input, accessibility, etc. </p>
    <p>That's why POPULUS was born, it was made to help you setting up complete text inputs to build demos and experiments faster!</p>
